s://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25265334/))\\n\\n* **Gene product name and ID to be annotated to this term**\\nbiosynthetic pathway: Q0CJ62 Q0CJ60 Q0CJ58 Q0CJ57 Q0CJ54 Q0CJ59\\n+ve regulation: Q0CJ56\\n\\n* **Parent term(s)**\\nbiosynthetic pathway: \\nGO:0019748 secondary metabolite biosynthetic process\\n+ve reg:\\nGO:1900376 regulation of secondary metabolite biosynthetic process\\n\\nthe authors say that terreic acid is a  \\\"a quinone epoxide\\\" so there might be other suitable parents?\\n\\n\\n\",\n  \"comments\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws7grfDP\",\n      \"author\": {\n        \"login\": \"ValWood\"\n      },\n      \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n      \"body\": \"CHEBI:156546\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-01-19T17:34:31Z\",\n      \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n      \"isMinimized\": false,\n      \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n      \"reactionGroups\": [],\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31114#issuecomment-3769495759\",\n      \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws7grkR-\",","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"__issue_context__.json","time":{"start":1778975970246,"end":1778975970263}},"id":"prt_e333b13bd001CzwdwpXs8Ec5N8","sessionID":"ses_1ccc5124fffelzMFVLcElI37gx","messageID":"msg_e333b03fe001FQ4A2sOcaH7gNO"}}
